<inglise> (23) Whereas cooperation should be strengthened with the competent international organizations, including the World Health Organization (WHO) and the Organization for Economic Cooperation and Development (OECD), and with non-member countries; whereas other bodies, such as non-governmental organizations, may also have a role to play; </inglise>
